      <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/reference/r_cli-options.dita" xtrc="p:2;114:10">Starts the interactive REPL for rule development and debugging. No
      options are required. See the
      <xref href="../../rule-creator-guide/reference/r_repl-commands.dita" class="- topic/xref " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/reference/r_cli-options.dita" xtrc="xref:1;116:90" type="reference"><?ditaot gentext?>REPL commands reference<?ditaot genshortdesc?><desc class="- topic/desc ">Complete reference for all commands available in the   <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/rule-creator-guide/reference/r_repl-commands.dita" xtrc="codeph:1;23:11">md-validate repl</codeph> interactive session.</desc></xref>
